Device contains two National Semiconductor DP83815s (DP83815DVNG) for two ethernet connections
[http://www.idt.com/?partID=79RC32V332-150DH 79RC32V332-150DH part page]
The default SSID of these access points is the last three octets of the MAC address (lower case letters).
ID/OD measurements may not be exact
